    "have diverse effects on the collection of text-based data.",
    "Specifically, the lack of sequential characteristics leads to the most significant loss in accuracy in the PTC dataset, underscoring the importance of obtaining relationships between words that appear close to each other in brief texts.",
    "Nevertheless, the lack of syntactic or semantic features resulted in a significant decrease in accuracy throughout the three datasets, highlighting their importance in detecting word dependencies across vast gaps and interpreting multiple meanings of words.",
    "In order to promote and confirm the efficacy of multiclass Intra-Inter graph Information Propagation and Enhancement, we performed ablation tests on three datasets, specifically examining two key aspects: RDEP and ADMF.",
    "Within this part, we have created two different versions of H-GIN: H-GIN (RDEP) and H-GIN (ADMF)."
